    AL_006_Check -->|No| AL_006_Fix[Fix Issues]
    AL_006_Fix --> AL_006

    AL_007[AL_007: Create plan enforcement tests<br/>Agent: test-builder<br/>Target: test_plan_enforcement.py] --> AL_007_Check{Success?}
    AL_007_Check -->|Yes| AL_008
    AL_007_Check -->|No| AL_007_Fix[Fix Issues]
